openconsensus.tags

Interface TagMap

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyTagMap

    @Immutable
public interface TagMap
    A map from TagKey to TagValue and TagMetadata that can be used to label anything that is associated with a specific operation.

    For example, TagMaps can be used to label stats, log messages, or debugging information.

    Since:
    0.1.0
